# Calculator

> Perform basic math operations

[![PyPI Version][pypi-image]][pypi-url]


`Calculator` performs:
 - addition
 - subraction
 - multiplication
 - division
 - n root of a number

## Installation

```sh
pip install calculator_ab
```

## Usage

Initiate Calculator:

```python
>>> import calculator_ab
```

